## Verification Plan

### Automated
- `npm run dev` — check no import/compilation errors
- Visual: confirm all 14 nodes render with correct GLB models
- Visual: confirm power lines connect correct nodes
- Visual: confirm entity-type telemetry renders in ExplainabilityPanel

### Manual Verification
1. Time-of-day cycle: solar output rises/falls correctly
2. EV charging surge at 18:00: smart meter demand spikes
3. Coal plant RPM tracks 50Hz sync (3000 RPM at balance)
4. RMU self-healing: trigger a fault, watch breaker trip → ring path activates
5. Cyber intrusion flag: random RED alert on HV substation
6. Dist. transformer lifespan decaying under overload
7. AI advisor triggers on cyber intrusion + fault events

